{"title":"闹春耕","authors":["欧阳翎"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":4,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹春耕（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欧阳翎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽晴忽雨岭南天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一高一低粤北田；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯弯路，曲曲烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几缕春阳，嵌在山那边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山那边，瓦房一大片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白的是墙，红的是檐；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村前瓜——坠坠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村后果——串串。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见人影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不闻鸟喧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见娃娃在塘边牧鸭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉在树下抽烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问娃娃，人去哪里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问老汉，鸟飞哪边？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们指我上山巅——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，山巅好片天："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田水漫漫，软土绵绵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日落水中，彩霞浮水面；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人喊，牛叫，鞭儿响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳雀声高，布谷声啭……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄泥腿，春风脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——晃晃，动动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男人竹笠，女人汗巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——飘飘，闪闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铲泥、挑土、撒金谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?牛、扶犁、绣金田；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风带露润人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春阳艳红火朝天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎春风，赶春潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男男女女干劲添，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹起一个，山区新生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹出一个，公社大丰年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插秧姑娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山绿，没有秧苗绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天蓝，没有田水蓝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴竹笠，卷裤管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘插秧在田间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一株一株苗，翠滴滴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插绿了田垅，插圆了波浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘的手，是画家的彩笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"描出了水纹、绿秧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然落下一阵云雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田水叮咚，禾苗蹦蹦长；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刹那换过一阵阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾苗伸长绿色的臂膀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥姑娘的手这快、这巧？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为她心里有幅丰收的图案；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥禾苗长得这快、这欢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为公社的土肥、水美、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天宽……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}